OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with occasional rain in
OL,6,Fthe morning then brightening up with a
OL,7,Ffew showers. Persistent rain returning
OL,8,Ffrom the west from late afternoon
OL,9,Fonwards, some heavy with strengthening
OL,10,Fsouth to southwest winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe evening starting cloudy
OL,13,Fwith rain then turning clearer and
OL,14,Fdrier from the west for a time.
OL,15,FOccasional showers then setting in
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
