OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FFrequent blustery showers
OL,6,Fand gale force winds. A brighter
OL,7,Fafternoon with more sunny intervals
OL,8,Fbut still some showers. Winds slowly
OL,9,Feasing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,12,Frain then blustery showers on
OL,13,FThursday, gales. Colder with sunshine
OL,14,Fand showers on Friday. Remaining
OL,15,Fshowery on Saturday.
